metadata.name: Lucky Dollar Metaverse
metadata.description: LDM is a collection of 1,000,000 Lucky Dollar Metaverse NFTs, unique digital collectibles living on the Ethereum blockchain. Your lucky dollar works as a membership card and provides access to benefits for members only, the first of which is access to a private raffle with multiple benefits. Future areas and benefits can be unlocked by the community by activating the roadmap.
